title: Angels of Change 2015
desc: Angels of Change is an annual event highlighting the strengths of the Trans community by promoting visibility. ?Each year we celebrate youth who have participated in the Center for Transyouth Health and Development at the ?Division of Adolescent and Young Adult Medicine, Children's Hospital Los Angeles, and taken part in a leadership program. ?The event will introduce this year's angels as well as two selected families. ?We are thrilled that this year, the program has been developed in partnership with youth and will be hosted ?by celebrity guests Candis Cayne and Chandi Moore as seen in "I Am Cait".
